::Battera::
She swooped down from the rafters in the hanger bay and landed.  She walked 
slowly to the door way of Scorponok's lab.  She used her night vision to 
look around the door way.  She saw nothing.  She peered inside the lab using 
her night vision.  She didn't see anything but senced that something was 
inside.
She yelled into the room, "Who are you? What are you doing here?"
She drew her dagger and kept it at her side.
